Meghan Markle, Duchess of Sussex, revealed in the 2020 interview with Oprah Winfrey that Kate Middleton, Duchess of Cambridge made her cry during a bridesmaid fitting. Kate extended an olive branch to Meghan in the form of flowers, which she misunderstood as an apology, a friend of Prince William has claimed. They told Daily Mail: "It obviously never occurred [to Meghan] that they were a peace offering, not an apology." They added: "Despite much provocation, both William and Catherine have tried to keep the peace more than anyone will ever realise." FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES...